{
  "_doc": "Single source of truth for the FX/backdrop strip. `global` = generic FX rules applied to EVERY rig's THUMBNAIL only. `per_slug` = extra patterns applied to BOTH pose and thumb (use only when the backdrop is so large it wrecks the pose auto-fit framing — currently c1067_s02 Tamarinne stage). `per_slug_thumb_only` = extra patterns applied to the THUMBNAIL ONLY, leaving the detail-page pose.png with its full scene intact (c5128 Hwayoung beach, c5175 Aram sky). Read by tools/render.html (fetch), tools/render_thumbs.js (pre-filter), site/viewer.html ('Hide FX' toggle = global ∪ per_slug ∪ per_slug_thumb_only). All patterns compile case-insensitive. Scene patterns deliberately EXCLUDE lens-clip slots (bb_*/glass_light*). NOT the same as slot_excludes.json (permanent always-hidden junk).",
